description: This common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 60, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 120, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Stringalong for East, 3 for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [120 Votes, Common]
